description: Try our easy to follow Grape, Almond & Yoghurt Cake recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Grape, Almond & Yoghurt Cake Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Pour cake batter into pan. Press grapes into mixture. Bake for 40 minutes or until cooked when tested with a skewer. Cool for 20 minutes before removing from pan. Cut into wedges and serve drizzled with honey and, if desired, extra yoghurt.
